Class BodyGeom

java.lang.Object
  vehiclesimulationcore.BodyGeom
class BodyGeom
extends java.lang.Object

Title: Vehicle Dynamics Simulation Program

Description: vehicle dynmaics, braking system simulation

Copyright: Copyright (c) 2006 Faculty of Information Technology Engineering at Damascus University

body geomerty holds a branch group of it's body components and additional dim data in general the body is not changed, because we change it's parent transform group how ever when enabling the suspension mechanics, we'll change it relatively to the whole vehicle
